{"surah":91,"verses":[{"n":1,"key":"91:1","arabic":" وَٱلشَّمْسِ وَضُحَىٰهَا","page":595,"juz":30,"en":"By the sun and its brightness","id":"Demi matahari dan sinarnya pada pagi hari,","words":[{"a":"وَٱلشَّمْسِ","en":"By the sun","id":"demi matahari"},{"a":"وَضُحَىٰهَا","en":"and its brightness","id":"dan cahayanya pagi hari"}]},{"n":2,"key":"91:2","arabic":"وَٱلْقَمَرِ إِذَا تَلَىٰهَا","page":595,"juz":30,"en":"And [by] the moon when it follows it","id":"demi bulan apabila mengiringinya,","words":[{"a":"وَٱلْقَمَرِ","en":"And the moon","id":"dan bulan"},{"a":"إِذَا","en":"when","id":"apabila"},{"a":"تَلَىٰهَا","en":"it follows it","id":"mengiringinya"}]},{"n":3,"key":"91:3","arabic":"وَٱلنَّهَارِ إِذَا جَلَّىٰهَا","page":595,"juz":30,"en":"And [by] the day when it displays it","id":"demi siang apabila menampakkannya,","words":[{"a":"وَٱلنَّهَارِ","en":"And the day","id":"dan siang"},{"a":"إِذَا","en":"when","id":"apabila"},{"a":"جَلَّىٰهَا","en":"it displays it","id":"menampakkannya"}]},{"n":4,"key":"91:4","arabic":"وَٱلَّيْلِ إِذَا يَغْشَىٰهَا","page":595,"juz":30,"en":"And [by] the night when it covers [i.e., conceals] it","id":"demi malam apabila menutupinya (gelap gulita),","words":[{"a":"وَٱلَّيْلِ","en":"And the night","id":"dan malam"},{"a":"إِذَا","en":"when","id":"apabila"},{"a":"يَغْشَىٰهَا","en":"it covers it","id":"menutupinya"}]},{"n":5,"key":"91:5","arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ وَمَا بَنَىٰهَا","page":595,"juz":30,"en":"And [by] the sky and He who constructed it","id":"demi langit serta perancangannya (yang menakjubkan),","words":[{"a":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ","en":"And the heaven","id":"dan langit"},{"a":"وَمَا","en":"and (He) Who","id":"dan apa"},{"a":"بَنَىٰهَا","en":"constructed it","id":"pembinaannya"}]},{"n":6,"key":"91:6","arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ وَمَا طَحَىٰهَا","page":595,"juz":30,"en":"And [by] the earth and He who spread it","id":"demi bumi serta penghamparannya,","words":[{"a":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ","en":"And the earth","id":"dan bumi"},{"a":"وَمَا","en":"and by (He) Who","id":"dan apa"},{"a":"طَحَىٰهَا","en":"spread it","id":"penghamparannya"}]},{"n":7,"key":"91:7","arabic":"وَنَفْسٍ وَمَا سَوَّىٰهَا","page":595,"juz":30,"en":"And [by] the soul and He who proportioned it","id":"demi jiwa serta penyempurnaan (ciptaan)nya,","words":[{"a":"وَنَفْسٍۢ","en":"And (the) soul","id":"dan manusia/jiwa"},{"a":"وَمَا","en":"and (He) Who","id":"dan apa"},{"a":"سَوَّىٰهَا","en":"proportioned it","id":"penyempurnaanya"}]},{"n":8,"key":"91:8","arabic":"فَأَلْهَمَهَا فُجُورَهَا وَتَقْوَىٰهَا","page":595,"juz":30,"en":"And inspired it [with discernment of] its wickedness and its righteousness,","id":"maka Dia mengilhamkan kepadanya (jalan) kejahatan dan ketakwaannya,","words":[{"a":"فَأَلْهَمَهَا","en":"And He inspired it","id":"maka Dia mengilhamkan padanya"},{"a":"فُجُورَهَا","en":"(to distinguish) its wickedness","id":"kedurhakaanya"},{"a":"وَتَقْوَىٰهَا","en":"and its righteousness","id":"dan ketaqwaannya"}]},{"n":9,"key":"91:9","arabic":"قَدْ أَفْلَحَ مَن زَكَّىٰهَا","page":595,"juz":30,"en":"He has succeeded who purifies it,","id":"sungguh beruntung orang yang menyucikannya (jiwa itu),","words":[{"a":"قَدْ","en":"Indeed","id":"sesungguhnya"},{"a":"أَفْلَحَ","en":"he succeeds","id":"beruntung"},{"a":"مَن","en":"who","id":"siapa/orang"},{"a":"زَكَّىٰهَا","en":"purifies it","id":"mensucikannya"}]},{"n":10,"key":"91:10","arabic":"وَقَدْ خَابَ مَن دَسَّىٰهَا","page":595,"juz":30,"en":"And he has failed who instills it [with corruption].","id":"dan sungguh rugi orang yang mengotorinya.","words":[{"a":"وَقَدْ","en":"And indeed","id":"dan sesungguhnya"},{"a":"خَابَ","en":"he fails","id":"celaka/rugi"},{"a":"مَن","en":"who","id":"orang"},{"a":"دَسَّىٰهَا","en":"buries it","id":"mengotorinya"}]},{"n":11,"key":"91:11","arabic":"كَذَّبَتْ ثَمُودُ بِطَغْوَىٰهَآ","page":595,"juz":30,"en":"Thamūd denied [their prophet] by reason of their transgression,","id":"(Kaum) Samud telah mendustakan (rasulnya) karena mereka melampaui batas (zalim),","words":[{"a":"كَذَّبَتْ","en":"Denied","id":"telah mendustakan"},{"a":"ثَمُودُ","en":"Thamud","id":"Samud"},{"a":"بِطَغْوَىٰهَآ","en":"by their transgression","id":"dan melampui batas"}]},{"n":12,"key":"91:12","arabic":"إِذِ ٱنۢبَعَثَ أَشْقَىٰهَا","page":595,"juz":30,"en":"When the most wretched of them was sent forth.","id":"ketika bangkit orang yang paling celaka di antara mereka,","words":[{"a":"إِذِ","en":"When","id":"ketika"},{"a":"ٱنۢبَعَثَ","en":"(was) sent forth","id":"bangkit"},{"a":"أَشْقَىٰهَا","en":"(the) most wicked of them","id":"orang yang lebih celaka diantaranya"}]},{"n":13,"key":"91:13","arabic":"فَقَالَ لَهُمْ رَسُولُ ٱللَّهِ نَاقَةَ ٱللَّهِ وَسُقْيَـٰهَا","page":595,"juz":30,"en":"And the messenger of Allāh [i.e., Ṣāliḥ] said to them, \"[Do not harm] the she-camel of Allāh or [prevent her from] her drink.\"","id":"lalu Rasul Allah (Saleh) berkata kepada mereka, \"(Biarkanlah) unta betina dari Allah ini dengan minumannya.\"","words":[{"a":"فَقَالَ","en":"But said","id":"dan berkata"},{"a":"لَهُمْ","en":"to them","id":"kepada mereka"},{"a":"رَسُولُ","en":"(the) Messenger","id":"rasul"},{"a":"ٱللَّهِ","en":"(of) Allah","id":"Allah"},{"a":"نَاقَةَ","en":"(It is the) she-camel","id":"unta betina"},{"a":"ٱللَّهِ","en":"(of) Allah","id":"Allah"},{"a":"وَسُقْيَـٰهَا","en":"and her drink","id":"dan minumannya"}]},{"n":14,"key":"91:14","arabic":"فَكَذَّبُوهُ فَعَقَرُوهَا فَدَمْدَمَ عَلَيْهِمْ رَبُّهُم بِذَنۢبِهِمْ فَسَوَّىٰهَا","page":595,"juz":30,"en":"But they denied him and hamstrung her. So their Lord brought down upon them destruction for their sin and made it equal [upon all of them].","id":"Namun mereka mendustakannya dan menyembelihnya, karena itu Tuhan membinasakan mereka karena dosanya, lalu diratakan-Nya (dengan tanah).","words":[{"a":"فَكَذَّبُوهُ","en":"But they denied him","id":"dan mendustakan"},{"a":"فَعَقَرُوهَا","en":"and they hamstrung her","id":"maka mereka melukai/menyembelih"},{"a":"فَدَمْدَمَ","en":"So destroyed","id":"maka menurunkan azab/membinasakan"},{"a":"عَلَيْهِمْ","en":"them","id":"atas mereka"},{"a":"رَبُّهُم","en":"their Lord","id":"Tuhan mereka"},{"a":"بِذَنۢبِهِمْ","en":"for their sin","id":"dengan dosa-dosa mereka"},{"a":"فَسَوَّىٰهَا","en":"and leveled them","id":"dan Dia meratakannya"}]},{"n":15,"key":"91:15","arabic":"وَلَا يَخَافُ عُقْبَـٰهَا","page":595,"juz":30,"en":"And He does not fear the consequence thereof.","id":"Dan Dia tidak takut terhadap akibatnya.","words":[{"a":"وَلَا","en":"And not","id":"dan tidak"},{"a":"يَخَافُ","en":"He fears","id":"takut"},{"a":"عُقْبَـٰهَا","en":"its consequences","id":"akibatnya"}]}]}